highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 217 weeks straight.
Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Peaches (feat. Daniel Caesar & Giveon)” is the highest at #1.
“HOLIDAY” by Lil Nas X is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 75 spots at #82.
“MONTERO (Call Me By Your Name)” by Lil Nas X is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
